h4. Actor:
Remittance User.

h4. Description: 
Name of use case represent its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [ARMS|guide:_ShowARMSPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Disbursment" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click "Task Instrument Mapping" link.
* [Show Landing page of "Task Instrument Mapping"|guide:ShowForMapTaskActionService].
* Select "Process Type" from drop-down list.
* Select "Instrument Type" from drop-down list.
* Populate "Instrument Wise Bank" List in drop-down.

h4. Pre-condition: 
* User must have "Refresh bank dropDown" privilege.

h4. Process: 
* Get "Instrument Wise Bank" list from server.

h4. Post-condition: 

* *Success:*
** Populate all "Instrument Wise Bank" list in drop down.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

